+		 * mdev->ldev member. Double check, and short-circuit to endio.
+		 * In case the last activity log transaction failed to get on
+		 * stable storage, and this is a WRITE, we may not even submit
+		 * this bio. */
+		if (get_ldev(mdev)) {
